sentences.english: The plane was full of holiday-makers.

sentences.chinese: 過去九龍城寨附近有一箇舊的飛機場。

sentences.english: One key element is his choice of airports.
sentences.chinese: 一個閉頭要素是他對飛機場狄住擇。

sentences.english: Over the next 10 years it plans to build dozens of new airports.
sentences.chinese: 接下來的10年裏，中國還計劃建設數十家新飛機場。

sentences.english: The airport is north-east of the centre.

sentences.english: Can I get it at the airport?
sentences.chinese: 我可以在飛機場買到嗎？

sentences.chinese: 我更喜歡那飛機場和附近的兩座小山丘。

sentences.english: A taxi directly from the airport to the Dali Hump will cost around 100RMB.

你需要有人在飛機場接你嗎？

sentences.english: They bused the tourists to the airport.
sentences.chinese: 他們用公共汽車把旅遊者運送到飛機場。

sentences.english: The coach leaves for the airport at 0815.
sentences.chinese: 民航汽車15出發去飛機場。
